{"title":"见了困难迎头闯","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"见了困难迎头闯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸盆端水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开钻缺水真着急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻井工人创奇迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲冰凿洞取湖水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸盆端水排几里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直端得：湖水见泥井见底；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见那：泥浆哗哗奔流急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一口油井又钻成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造条件得胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴风雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中雷猛电迅天欲塌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑云滚滚压井架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风如虎啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨似开闸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鹰收了翅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狼兔早归“家”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻台上怎么样？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈，该干啥还干啥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻工打大钳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司钻握刹把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"操作和晴天一个样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻头直往地心里扎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意志比钻头还坚硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲憋足了一百个大气压！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭它风狂雨暴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣湿三层照样把井打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻机高唱胜利歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风败雨退现早霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一口优质井已打成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进了一个步伐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心为油田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳正当午，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗滴荒原土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心为油田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红不畏苦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎面刮风砂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨响哗哗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心为石油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦又算啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好马劲在腿上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命者的劲就在闯上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯就能闯出成绩来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯就能闯出经验来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯就能闯出道路来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井越深越有打头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山越高越有奔头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难越多越有闯头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任务越重越有干头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井越深越有打头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真金不怕火炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真金不怕火炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏不怕严寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄面前无困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干革命就要挑重担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功夫出自磨炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇迹创自平凡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心专世上无难事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟党走能闯万重关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北风当电扇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身穿冰结凌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪吹不进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活出大汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北风当电扇。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}